{
  "stem": "747.5",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And the edge of the village was a single house.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And we decided that we up on-- and-- but no matter what, that's it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So we climbed up on the-- where the animals are, and we dug ourselves into the hay.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And we tried to fall asleep.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And all of the sudden we heard French speaking-- talking in the yard, and the heavenly smell of coffee coming up.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And the hunger was so great that we just couldn't go to sleep.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And one by one, we came down.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And we find out that they were French prisoners of war-- soldiers.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Lovely young men.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And they were telling us-- well, they noticed right away because we had a red-- a red cross painted in our back.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And the coat, what we were wearing, one sleeve, had to be taken out and change it with someone else's.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "So I had a navy blue coat, and had one green sleeve in it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "That in case, if I want to run away, it was so obvious, that it's so ridiculous, that outfit, I couldn't go far.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they knew who we are, and they were telling us that the Russian army's right behind us.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they probably will get in that night to the town, to the village.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And if you know what the Russians are doing to the women?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we didn't know anything, but we were frightened enough to-- when they offered, that if we want to help them to push, they open-- broke into a-- a food depot.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they had bread-- enough bread and coffee.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So they gave us a big slice of bread and a mug of coffee.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
